<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>كِتَابُ الْحُدُودِ وَمَا يُحْذَرُ مِنَ الْحُدُودِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">بَابٌ:</span> لَا يُشْرَبُ الْخَمْرُ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَقَالَ ابْنُ عَبَّاسٍ يُنْزَعُ مِنْهُ نُورُ الْإِيمَانِ فِي الزِّنَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>